      "text": "建前上、マネージャーが必要だとは分かりますけど……\nくれぐれも、余計な口出しはしないようお願いします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand that we need a manager for appearances‚ but…\nPlease refrain from unnecessary interference.",
